// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2024-0040 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: bb63c14c-7dff-594e-b3c5-8f8c6327d0da

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*amazonlinux:2023*" or process.executable like~ "*azure linux:3.0*" or process.executable like~ "*cbl-mariner:2.0*" or process.executable like~ "*chainguard:*" or process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:7*")
